Detailed Description

Description:
: TLC to test dynamic allocation APIs exposed o TAs and TLs Trustlet TlTestMemory.

Test the Tl memory functions tlApiMalloc,tlApiFree,tlApiRealloc, memset, memmove, memcmp

TestCase_05_TestMemory_MemCompare ( )
Trusted Applications dependencies:
08060308060501020000000000000000
Focus:
memcmp
Test Steps:
Test memcmp
  • Call tlApiMalloc(100, 0) -> ptr1; Call tlApiMalloc(100, 0) -> ptr2;
  • Call memcmp(ptr1, ptr2, 100), should return 0
  • Set ptr1[0] = 0x01
  • Call memcmp(ptr1, ptr2, 100), should return a positive number
  • Set ptr[0] = 0x02
  • Call memcmp(ptr1, ptr2, 100), should return a negative number
